## Window Functions vs GROUP BY

| | `GROUP BY` | Window Function |
|---|---|---|
| Rows returned | Collapsed (one per group) | All original rows preserved |
| Mix aggregate + row detail? | No | Yes |
| Typical use case | Summary reports | Rankings, running totals, peer comparisons |

