## Quick Reference Cheatsheet

| Function | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `ROW_NUMBER()` | Unique sequential rank, no ties |
| `RANK()` | Rank with gaps after ties |
| `DENSE_RANK()` | Rank without gaps after ties |
| `NTILE(n)` | Split into n buckets |
| `LAG(col, n, default)` | Value from n rows before |
| `LEAD(col, n, default)` | Value from n rows after |
| `SUM/AVG/COUNT/MIN/MAX() OVER (...)` | Aggregate without collapsing rows |
| `FIRST_VALUE()` | First value in the window frame |
| `LAST_VALUE()` | Last value in the window frame (needs explicit frame!) |

